{"tid":1996431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世衛駐華代表︰中方拒絕世衛參與調查病毒來源","createTime":"2020-05-01T03:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T03:28:44.000Z","uid":30561,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d39815c22077ac860d78429adeec510f356b87cb","tid":1996431,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T03:20:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=389523&amp;fbclid=IwAR35wjfsZ_-ZWDPR96gjp_sXaAWOAmcDoepnyc457hOqwFS1fSk2syw-fnk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D389523%26fbclid%3DIwAR35wjfsZ_-ZWDPR96gjp_sXaAWOAmcDoepnyc457hOqwFS1fSk2syw-fnk&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=c191c7a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D389523%26fbclid%3DIwAR35wjfsZ_-ZWDPR96gjp_sXaAWOAmcDoepnyc457hOqwFS1fSk2syw-fnk&h=e3478e32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=389523&amp;fbclid=IwAR35wjfsZ_-ZWDPR96gjp_sXaAWOAmcDoepnyc457hOqwFS1fSk2syw-fnk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://external.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?w=750&amp;h=391&amp;url=fbstaging%3A%2F%2Fgraph.facebook.com%2Fstaging_resources%2FMDEyNTcxMjc1ODg5OTMzODg6MTM3NzUwODE3MQ%3D%3D&amp;cfs=1&amp;ext=jpg&amp;_nc_hash=AQAuwHj8nKJH4GB_\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fw%3D750%26h%3D391%26url%3Dfbstaging%253A%252F%252Fgraph.facebook.com%252Fstaging_resources%252FMDEyNTcxMjc1ODg5OTMzODg6MTM3NzUwODE3MQ%253D%253D%26cfs%3D1%26ext%3Djpg%26_nc_hash%3DAQAuwHj8nKJH4GB_&h=fd809803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】世衛駐華代表高力表示，世衛多次要求參與調查新型冠狀病毒來源，但遭到中方拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n高力接受英國天空新聞訪問，指知道中方已經開始就新型冠狀病毒疫情進行調查，但未有邀請世衛參與。而世衛多次向中方衞生部門要求加入調查工作，但都被中方在沒有合理原因下拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n高力強調，調查清楚病毒來源以及動物透過甚麼媒介將病毒傳給人類，對防止再次發生疫情非常重要。他又指根據世衛現時得到的資料顯示，病毒源自武漢，相信是自然變種，而非人為製造出來的病毒。"},{"pid":"53750affee7bee64814bcff47f97ba0307d990e4","tid":1996431,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T03:21:21.000Z","msg":"割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4c45ca8f2b4b8541edfb93ffa34bf3bd773055","tid":1996431,"uid":173945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T03:28:44.000Z","msg":"世衛：我又唔夠錢洗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}